originalText.text: I’m a senior of 76 years, a patient of Dr. Jumani Krishnan for the past two years.  I have enjoyed and benefited greatly from the excellent professional care I received.  Dr. Krishnan is dedicated to providing medical and emotional wellness to her patients.  She listens to my concerns and explains in detail options and resources to aid and optimize my medical experience.  I am very grateful for Dr. Krishnan and hold her in the highest esteem.
